{"tid":2098296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警回覆梁柏堅：我地用既係叫加左照明證既激光瞄準器 唔係雷射槍所以無問題！","createTime":"2020-07-07T11:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:14:22.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec4265260c8c7dc24f9da448ee9d493acfc024b","tid":2098296,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a38VgH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa38VgH4.jpg&h=2b07ef6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛收到警方回覆我6月9號中環拍攝到警方使用雷射裝置照射人群嘅回信。差佬話自己用嘅叫激光瞄準器（市民用嘅叫雷射槍）。￼而今日有個女仔喺被拘捕現場身上搵唔到「雷射槍」證物￼，咁都可以被判監三個月￼。今日收到差佬依封掛號信更加覺得內容諷刺...￼<br />\n<br />\n成日叫區議員支持警察工作去支持法治，唔該07/08雙普選特區政府跟咗憲法未？真係講到自己都覺得口又臭又嘥氣⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n#裁判官話必須要向市民清楚表達訊息<br />\n#表達法治已死n次<br />\n#不停出信去指出荒謬自己都覺得自己荒謬<br />\n#雷射瞄準器 #激光槍￼￼￼<br />\n#成日叫人守規矩唔該最有權力嗰班守規矩先￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/168187426856933/posts/1215062202169445/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F168187426856933%2Fposts%2F1215062202169445%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivd9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=79bb9f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/168187426856933/posts/1215062202169445/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7dc0eb698ba36d2aa1de2dc077bd268ed028a494","tid":2098296,"uid":60131,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"「激光」同「鐳射」有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02faf223d147e8db479d8a3ff7e6766d9dfce8cf","tid":2098296,"uid":85552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dc0eb698ba36d2aa1de2dc077bd268ed028a494","tid":2098296,"uid":60131,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"「激光」同「鐳射」有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo